            "text": "MASTER OF ME \nDir by: @andremuir \n\nOne of the early masters I was exposed to was @queenlatifah. Her love and dedication for the community created a life long legacy and stood as an example of everything I wanted to be. \n\nMy book Master of Me is a narrative curriculum on how I have integrated the fragmented aspect of who I am and accepted them as one. Leading me, to a life full of service and purpose. If you’d like to read it’s currently available for pre-order! Link in Bio 🫶🏾🫶🏾🫶🏾"
