          "caption": {
            "has_translation": null,
            "created_at": 1732238376,
            "pk": "17935971182826303",
            "text": "The conversation at @apollotheater was amazing last night. @michaelstrahan I couldn’t have done it without you. You have been a friend, brother and a mentor to me. Teaching me the essence of hustling and enjoying life when we can. Also being frugal cause I’m cheaper than you! Haha I love you for always seeing my value and never ever not encouraging my power.\n\nI love my friends so much. They ALWAYS show up for me, even in the ways I didn’t know I needed. Special shout out to my girl @voguebritt, since we were teenagers she would find ways to help me exist outside of work. Remind me that I could have normalcy and my life didn’t have to revolve around the industry, constantly extending her community to me.\n\nI have such immense gratitude for my community because there is no self mastery without it! Who’s your community? 💕🥰🙏🏾"
          },
